1. *Prilazi* mi neka devojka. (*Approaching* me is some girl.) 
2. On *prilazi* školi. (He *approaches* the school.) 
3. Kada *prilaziš* kući? (When are you *approaching* home?)
4. *Prilazeći* restoranu, osetio je miris hrane. ( *Approaching* the restaurant, he smelled the food.)
5. Moramo *prilaziti* ovom problemu na različite načine. (We must *approach* this problem in different ways.)
6. Njegov *prilaz* zgradi je uvek čist. (His *entrance* to the building is always clean.)
7. Oni su *prilazili* novcu na nelegalan način. (They *approached* money in an illegal way.)
8. Postoji više *prilaza* gradu. (There are several *approaches* to the city.) 
9. *Prilazeći* vrhu planine, osetio je da mu nedostaje kiseonika. ( *Approaching* the top of the mountain, he felt short of oxygen.) 
10. Nisam siguran kako *pristupiti* ovom problemu, ali ćemo morati da *prilazimo* s oprezom. (I'm not sure how to *approach* this problem, but we'll have to *approach* it with caution.)